hopobject.body: A Second Class stamp cvs central square pharmacy hours Ouya's cash also will not be handed over all at once. Under the new plan, developers get this first 50% at the functioning beta stage. This should ensure only real viable projects get the money. Another 25% is dispersed at launch, and another 25% arrives at the end of the exclusivity period. About the exclusivity, Ouya now requires one month of exclusivity for each $10,000 of matching funds, up to six months. The bonus program that would have handed $100,000 to the highest earning campaign is gone completely. However, developers will be free to make a PC version of the game at any point.
